short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Feather, fork of SweezeBreeze tailored for usage with TBH.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
various keybindings for nationstates to assist in tag raiding

A: reload page
Q: go back
U: check if you updated
S: endorse nation
O: ban nation
K: eject nation
R: confirm wa join
F: move to region whose page you're currently on
B: move to DBZ
E: apply/resign to WA
W: go to current region page
D: appoint yourself as and/or deappoint ROs
